  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Client Manager",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for an outstanding Senior Client Manager to join our team in Singapore who will champion our high standards and contribute to our famous work for famous brands.</p><p>You will be at the heart of the team, using your client management expertise gained from a brand/packaging design agency to lead project work and strengthen our client relationships. You'll also be responsible for developing and mentoring the junior members of your team, helping them to achieve their full potential. As you'll be immersed in the creative process at all times, the right person for this role will be a bit like us - with meticulous attention to detail and has a true passion for brands, design, creativity and collaboration.</p><p>If this sounds like the perfect role for you, send us your CV and we'll take it from there.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
