    "description": "<p>Design Bridge is an international branding design agency with a passion for solving challenging brand problems with outstanding creativity and based on insightful understanding of our clients' brands and business issues. Our client services team consists of some of the most talented, pro-active and lovely people in the industry.<br />  <br />  We have over 300 people, and around 30 different nationalities. We have over 30 years' experience in the design and branding industry, offices in London, Amsterdam, Singapore and New York and we work in over 40 countries across the globe.</p>  ",
